data.description: Introducing a poetic three-bedroom, two-bathroom house located in the south part of Minneapolis. This modest home features a backyard and a detached two-stall garage, providing practical outdoor spaces. Step inside to discover an uncomplicated layout, offering everyday functionality. Situated in a convenient location in the south part of Minneapolis, this house offers a straightforward living experience.
